# Target Short-Range Order (SRO) Parameters for High-Entropy Alloy
# --------------------------------------------------------
# Format: Upper triangular matrix for 3 atom types (Fe-Mn-Cr)
#
# Matrix interpretation:
#   - Positive values: Promote clustering (like neighbors preferred)
#   - Negative values: Promote ordering (unlike neighbors preferred)
#   - Zero values: Random distribution
#
# First Shell Configuration:
#   - Slight Fe-Fe clustering (0.1)
#   - Fe-Mn ordering (-0.1)
#   - Mn-Mn slight clustering (0.05)
#   - Random distribution for Cr interactions
#
# Row 1: Fe-Fe
# Row 2: Fe-Mn  Mn-Mn
# Row 3: Fe-Cr  Mn-Cr  Cr-Cr
# Row 4: Co-Fe  Co-Mn  Co-Cr  Co-Co

